General.Name: EDU Holdings Ltd
General.Description: EDU Holdings Limited, through its subsidiaries, provides tertiary education services in Australia. The company offers vocational education and training services, including accredited certificate and diploma level courses in health and community services. It also provides higher education services in the areas of creative therapies, counselling and psychotherapy, and early childhood education. The company was formerly known as UCW Limited and changed its name to EDU Holdings Limited in December 2021. EDU Holdings Limited was incorporated in 2004 and is based in Sydney, Australia.
